---
name: equity-term-sheet
description: Drafts a U.S. equity financing term sheet for venture capital or private equity rounds, structured as a non-binding framework with binding confidentiality, exclusivity, expenses, and governing-law carveouts. Use for Series A/B/C or other preferred stock financings, investor rights negotiations, and pricing/valuation term sheets. Trigger keywords: term sheet, equity financing, Series A, preferred stock, VC, venture capital, private equity, investor rights, cap table.
